OL,3,CTeenager arrested after alleged
OL,4,Cassault involving hammer at school
OL,6,FA teenager has been arrested following
OL,7,Fan assault involving a hammer at a
OL,8,Fschool.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Redhill Academy,
OL,11,FArnold, in Nottinghamshire, shortly
OL,12,Fafter 9.45am on Monday after a pupil
OL,13,Fsuffered a head injury.
OL,15,FThe victim had allegedly been hit with
OL,16,Fa hammer.
OL,18,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment
OL,19,Fand his injuries aren't believed to be
OL,20,Flife-altering.
