OL,3,CTeenager arrested after alleged
OL,4,Cassault involving hammer at school
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been arrested at
OL,7,Fthe school on suspicion of causing
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm and possession of
OL,9,Fan offensive weapon. He remains in
OL,10,Fpolice custody.
OL,12,FSergeant Richard Craig, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "We
OL,14,Ftreat all reports involving weapons
OL,15,Fand violence with the utmost
OL,16,Fseriousness.
OL,18,F"A suspect has been arrested and we
OL,19,Fare now working to understand exactly
OL,20,Fwhat happened."
